title: War of the Roses: Who's hair ties were they?
description: Missy is wondering if her boyfriend is cheating on her because her dog got sick and when she brought him into the vet, they found hair ties in the dogs stomach.  Missy has short hair and never has hair ties around so now she thinks her boyfriend may have brought the dog around another girl with longer hair that would use hair ties.
